    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。标准TCP头部是20字节，但Options字段是变长的。您说的患者记录标识是要放在160-191位这个位置，替代传统的Options字段吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "160-191",
        "(HealthTech_PatientRecords)",
